      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">A Prakash Hyundai AMC gives you complete peace of mind — all periodic services covered at a fixed annual price with priority scheduling. Ideal for corporate fleets and daily commuters.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] text-lg">Small Car AMC</p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">i10 Nios, Grand i10</p>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#002C5F] mt-3">₹5,999<span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-400">/yr</span></p>
