      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-[#F5F6F7] rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Do I need a prior appointment for Hyundai service?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Walk-ins are accepted but we recommend booking via WhatsApp to secure a priority slot and reduce waiting time. Most bookings receive confirmation within 30 minutes during business hours.</p>
